---
---
<section class="anthropic-proof section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="anthropic-proof-header reveal">
      <h2>Até a Anthropic usa.</h2>
      <p>A empresa que criou o Claude usa Claude Code internamente para automatizar marketing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="anthropic-proof-card reveal" style="transition-delay:120ms">
      <div class="anthropic-proof-source">
        <span class="source-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="source-label">Anthropic · Blog Oficial</span>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="anthropic-proof-quote">
        O time de Growth Marketing da Anthropic cortou o tempo de criação de anúncios de 30 minutos para 30 segundos usando Claude Code.
      </blockquote>

      <div class="anthropic-proof-metrics">
        <span class="metric-badge">
          <span class="metric-old">30 min</span>
          <span class="metric-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="metric-new">30 seg</span>
        </span>
        <span class="metric-badge">Sem código</span>
      </div>

      <a
        href="https://claude.com/blog/how-anthropic-uses-claude-marketing"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="anthropic-proof-link"
      >
        Ler artigo completo →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .anthropic-proof-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .anthropic-proof-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .anthropic-proof-header p {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .anthropic-proof-card {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .anthropic-proof-source {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .source-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: pulse-dot 2s ease infinite;
  }
  .source-label {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .anthropic-proof-quote {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2.2vw, 20px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .anthropic-proof-metrics {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .metric-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-badge);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
  }
  .metric-old {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }
  .metric-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .metric-new {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .anthropic-proof-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .anthropic-proof-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .anthropic-proof-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
